select
  query_parameterized_hash,
  sum(t.num_queries) as num_queries,
  max_by(t.most_recent_query_info, interval_start_time) as most_recent_query_info,
  {
      'sum': sum(t.execution_time:sum::number),
      'min': min(t.execution_time:min::number),
      'max': max(t.execution_time:max::number),
      'avg': sum(t.execution_time:sum::number)::float / sum(t.num_queries)
  } as execution_time,
